title: Visit Springline's Dog Park & Enjoy Grooming + Pet Wash - Virtual Tour
posting_body: ['Welcome to Springline', 'Springline is redefining downtown Menlo Park.', 'Bringing a resort-style campus with culinary destinations, creative offices, modern residences and a mix of outdoor experiences.', "It's a destination and a journey - a place where you can collaborate and innovate, host clients, meet new people, live modern, share drinks and dinner, escape or encounter, and be a local in the coolest new neighborhood around.", 'Amenities Include:', 'Stainless Steel Appliance Suite with Gas Range, Electric Oven and Microwave', 'Chrome Pull-Down Kitchen Faucet', 'Dedicated Home Air Conditioning', 'Weathered Teak Cabinetry', 'Door Sensors, Smart Device Controls for Outlets and Lighting and Leak Detection', 'Backlit Majestic LED Mirror', 'Honeywell Smart Thermostats', 'Carrara-Inspired Quartz Countertops', 'Light Gray Subway Tile Backsplash', 'Delta & Kohler Fixtures', 'One complimentary Bike Parking Space', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>', '*Pricing and availability are subject to change daily.', 'Photos may not be of the exact advertised unit.', 'Please contact us today for the most up to date information!']
